                <h5>
                    Find Web Hosting</h5>
                <p>
                    You can easily find a web hosting company that offers the right mix of features
                    and price for your applications. Visit <a href="http://microsoft.com/web/hosting"
                        title="Microsoft/Web Website">Microsoft.com/web</a> to explore offerings from
                    many providers.
                </p>
                <p>
                    @(Html.ActionLink("Action", "Index", "Home", routeValues: null, htmlAttributes: new { @class = "btn btn-primary" }))
